   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 1 mark (AO2)</h5>\n<p><strong>Answer: C — Scarce resources</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>There was not enough supply of chips to satisfy demand — the definition of a scarce resource.</li>\n<li>'Unlimited wants' (D) describes the demand side in general, but the situation described is the shortage itself.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Examiner's Comments</h5>\n<p>The correct response to this question was Option C; however, many candidates gave Option D as the correct response.</p>\n</div>",
