   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 1 mark (AO1 1b)</h5>\n<p><strong>Answer: C — if the price falls, consumers buy more</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>The downward slope IS the law of demand: lower price, higher quantity demanded.</li>\n<li>A is about income (a shift factor, not shown here); B reverses cause and effect; D describes supply behaviour.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
