   "answer": 0,
   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 1 mark (AO1b)</h5>\n<p><strong>Answer: A — price and quantity will change in opposite directions</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Moving along a downward-sloping demand curve: price up → quantity demanded down, and vice versa — opposite directions.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Examiner's Comments</h5>\n<p>Most of the candidates gave A as the correct response to this question.</p>\n</div>",
   "modelAnswer": ""
