   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 1 mark (AO1b)</h5>\n<p><strong>Answer: B — The market demand curve shifts to the right</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Successful advertising raises willingness to buy at every price — a rightward shift of market demand. It acts on buyers, not on production costs, so supply is unaffected.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
