   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 1 mark (AO1 1b)</h5>\n<p><strong>Answer: C — Producers respond to changes in consumer demand</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Consumer sovereignty: demand signals steer production. State ownership (A) describes a planned economy, and competition is central, not absent (D).</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
   "modelAnswer": ""
