   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 1 mark (AO1a)</h5>\n<p><strong>Answer: D — Individuals cannot be producers of goods and services</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>This is FALSE (which makes it the answer): individuals like self-employed tradespeople are producers. The other three statements are true.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5>Examiner's Comments</h5>\n<p>The correct response was Option D. Incorrect responses ranged across the other three options and indicated some gaps in candidates' knowledge and understanding.</p>\n</div>",
   "modelAnswer": ""
