  "caseStudy": "<p>John is paid in twelve monthly instalments. Each month he earns £2,000 in gross pay minus deductions for income tax of £500.</p>",
  "hint": "Monthly net = £2,000 − £500 = £1,500. Then multiply by 12 months.",
