   "answer": 2,
   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 1 mark (AO1a)</h5>\n<p><strong>Answer: C — It only measures the price of goods</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>CPI covers goods AND services, so C is the false statement. It IS measured monthly, it IS based on an average family's spending, and it DOES use weighting.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Examiner's Comments</h5>\n<p>The emboldened word 'not' indicates that only C can be correct (the others are all true).</p>\n</div>",
