   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 1 mark (AO2)</h5>\n<p><strong>Answer: C — Increase investment in infrastructure</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Infrastructure investment is an actual policy tool that lowers costs and raises productive capacity. 'Increase economic growth' and 'increase foreign investment' are outcomes/goals, not policies; raising benefits works against the usual supply-side aim of increasing work incentives.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
   "modelAnswer": ""
